message.raw:
Made changes to queue.py to make it compatible with recent grafted commits
for deleting repeated shots. This removed the spielman fork's existing method
of overwriting old repeated shots.

Minor changes to the plugin code to make it put itself in an appropriate place
in the GUI, since the mainline and spielman GUI layouts are different.
